50
00:02:43,129 --> 00:02:44,864
I see.

51
00:02:46,132 --> 00:02:49,169
-He passed away last year.
-That's right.

52
00:02:49,235 --> 00:02:51,237
I really wanted to meet him once.

53
00:02:51,304 --> 00:02:53,406
Sadly, I couldn't.

54
00:02:54,974 --> 00:02:57,277
Shall we head inside?

55
00:02:57,343 --> 00:03:00,046
Let's go up to the second floor.

56
00:03:01,548 --> 00:03:03,183
Did Kitanofuji come here often?

57
00:03:03,249 --> 00:03:05,218
He came every summer.

58
00:03:05,285 --> 00:03:06,252
I see.

59
00:03:07,554 --> 00:03:09,856
Did you ever take up sumo yourself?

60
00:03:09,923 --> 00:03:12,725
I might look like I did, but I didn't.

61
00:03:12,792 --> 00:03:14,027
-You didn't?
-No.

62
00:03:14,093 --> 00:03:16,563
-Weren't you encouraged to try?
-I was,

63
