but I don't have the grit.

64
00:03:19,332 --> 00:03:23,870
This is from my uncle's
60th ring-entering ceremony.

65
00:03:23,937 --> 00:03:27,273
Even at sixty,
his physique was incredible.

66
00:03:27,340 --> 00:03:29,242
He looks strong.

67
