for hours to make the broth.

137
00:07:16,803 --> 00:07:20,106
I bet they take the broth
seriously here too.

138
00:07:20,173 --> 00:07:21,641
I'd think so.

139
00:07:21,707 --> 00:07:25,778
They even put
Kitanofuji's name on the sign.

140
00:07:25,845 --> 00:07:27,947
They can't serve sloppy chanko nabe.

141
00:07:28,014 --> 00:07:31,184
-That look says he won't forgive bad food.
-Right.

142
00:07:33,686 --> 00:07:34,620
